    "dialogue": [
        {
            "text": "Was it you who called me here? If you're in a bind, I can lend a hand. I'm Alm. Happy to be of service.",
            "context": "joined"
        },
        {
            "text": "So many Heroes here, and so many wearing such...exciting outfits! Has Celica worn anything like that too?",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "Even if the people recognize me as the heir to the throne, it still doesn't feel real to me... Still...I must do my best to live up to what's expected of my station.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "How many missions is that today? I don't enjoy sitting still either, but even you must rest sometime.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "This armor has been passed down through the generations in Rigel... It weighs...heavy on my shoulders.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "Even now, I can't neglect my training. The people of Rigel would reject me if I were to grow too weak, after all...",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I'm Alm. I've come to formally offer a greeting. And to admire this castle you have, <Player Name>.",
            "context": "friend"
        },
        {
            "text": "All right! I'm feeling nimble and ready. Let's keep this up!",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "If I'm to stand shoulder to shoulder with renowned heroes, I've got to grow even stronger than I am now!",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "I thought I felt some power well up inside me... Was it my imagination?",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "So this is my new ability, is it? I'll do my best to put it to good use.",
            "context": "growth"
        },
        {
            "text": "Growing up in a village, I never had to think about my country or how it fit in the world. That's why—to tell you the truth— I can't help but wonder if I'm truly meant for something like this... But still, I can't give up. I must forge ahead with all of my might, like when I was entrusted with the Deliverance. Besides, I have so many friends who are working alongside me: Celica, and my comrades in the Deliverance... And above all, the calls of those who brought me here drive me to build a world where we shape our own lives!",
            "context": "maxed"
        }
    ],
